sources.title: Attack from Outer Space 1965 | Sci-Fi Movie | Directed by Teruo Ishii | Colorized
sources.description:
Earth's savior unveils a cosmic conspiracy!
The superhero Starman is sent by the Emerald Planet to protect Earth from belligerent aliens from the Sapphire Galaxy. The Sapphireans (or “Spherions”) kidnap Dr. Yamanaka and force him to use his spaceship against the Earth.
 
Original title: Attack From Space (1965) AKA: Attack from Outer Space / Super Giant Vs the Satellites

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/xp9mHaWUxZ0


This film is subtitled in many languages.

Directors: Teruo Ishii, Koreyoshi Akasaka, Akira Mitsuwa
Writers: Ichirô Miyagawa
Cast: Ken Utsui, Sachihiro Ohsawa, Junko Ikeuchi
Genres: Colorized, Action, Sci-Fi


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles)
01:10 Interstellar conflict threatens Earth as advanced alien civilization prepares for invasion.
18:29 Invasion threat from outer space, scientist missing, Earth in danger, urgent action needed.
23:15 Interstellar battle ensues as resistance fights against impending destruction.
37:06 Intense space battle unfolds as Earth faces imminent destruction from alien forces.
52:25 In a space station, a doctor must make a life-changing decision to save his daughter and the Earth.
1:15:12 Farewells and goodbyes to friends and Starman with a touch of luck.
